{
  "stem": "11089.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 40.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was sent to a camp called, Landsberg, beside Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was known as [GERMAN], Camp Number 7.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- I-- I said, only two weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only two weeks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wanted us to keep four, but we behaved bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- it was a tremendous difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Birkenau, there was no hope to stay alive for the question of days, of hours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the-- in the labor camps, as long as you labored, as long as you worked properly, you-- they didn't kill you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But slowly, slowly, they made sure that you tire out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Less and less food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, when they saw you are-- cannot work anymore, like myself, they put you into a [GERMAN], in a sick people camp, beside Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was my next camp, called Kaufering, Lager IV.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked from August, till about end of January-- of-- of December.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I kept on working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Worked.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And as long as I worked, I was stealing, not from people, from fields, whatever I could, anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So but then, in Landsberg, until the rain didn't start with the snow, we used to go a shortcut to our work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shortcut.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the rain started, we had to go in a-- a long way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's when my shoes became with holes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Water came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- came in, and I had bruises all over my body, my feet.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Bruises from the dirt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, walking home from work, I just collapsed, because I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hit me with their rifle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What-- what could I do?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
